- "Bloomed" refers to feedback that has been resolved (is_resolved = 1);
- "Still growing" refers to feedback that has active priorities (priority_count > 1) and active categories (category_count > 1);
- "Gardeners" refers to the users who submitted the feedback;
- "Comments on the flowers" refers to the text comments in the feedback;
- "Planted" refers to the timestamp when the feedback was submitted;
- "Garden" refers to the application or service.

- 'Most recent active feedback' refers to the latest feedback submission by each user where the feedback is still active;
- 'Active feedback' is identified by the `is_active` flag in the `feedback_category_mapping` table being set to 1;
- 'Current status' is the latest status change recorded in the `feedback_status_history` table.

